*Vruće* sunce sija. (The *hot* sun is shining.)
Njegove *vruće* usne dodirnule su moje. (His *hot* lips touched mine.)
*Vruća* kafa je bila ukusna. (The *hot* coffee was delicious.)
Koliko god da se trudio, nije mogao da se zaštiti od *vrućeg* sunca. (No matter how hard he tried, he couldn't protect himself from the *hot* sun.)
*Vrući* asfalt je bio skoro neizdrživ. (The *hot* asphalt was almost unbearable.)